{"tid":2510143,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅西將在美洲盃前接種科興疫苗，全部由中工捐贈","createTime":"2021-04-30T02:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T03:26:35.000Z","uid":30040,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd7cb54f27038e4a6c33ff2d3084e6f7e0fe63e","tid":2510143,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"04月30日訊 根據TV3消息，梅西將在本賽季結束之後在巴塞羅那接種中國科興的新冠疫苗，隨後前往南美參加美洲杯。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">根據南美足聯的規定，參加本次阿根廷-哥倫比亞美洲杯的球員都需要接種疫苗</span>，而在歐洲踢球的國腳球員將收到南美足聯提供的免費疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n此前科興向南美足聯免費捐助了50000份疫苗，作為回應，梅西由南美足聯向科興公司代為送出了三件自己簽名的球衣。據南美足聯官員Gonzalo Belloso透露，科興公司的高管對於梅西非常欣賞和仰慕。"},{"pid":"d9de433df9a16f1b5b6ddff3d2d91f7762b78a1f","tid":2510143,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"@活著何求"},{"pid":"a2d38402529551b8acb0cad96a3b1c60a9bff39d","tid":2510143,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"rap"},{"pid":"cb2bc3185e541aac9d75107cb4544e16383862a9","tid":2510143,"uid":188249,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwpLWCg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuwpLWCg.gif&h=0bc693e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8920be36a1ea9bdebb7f8098cc8d0da77b0f391","tid":2510143,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"咁快去見老馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c5dc48d8fbaf15b4b2b734c63e7671fdd4e55d","tid":2510143,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:08:39.000Z","msg":"老馬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a588219b42b7d8f110fa3128858acfad73a7be63","tid":2510143,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:09:0